Kasancewar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da United Kingdom, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Kasuwancin yaduwar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) na nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Kingdomasar Ingila wanda ke tabbatar da cewa cutar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe, yayin da take faruwa a matakai daban-daban dangane da ƙasa.
Bisa ga gogewar da aka samu daga Italiya, ya kamata kasashe, asibitoci da kuma cibiyoyin kulawa mai zurfi su kara shirye-shiryen su don karuwar masu cutar COVID-19 da za su bukaci kulawar lafiya, musamman ma ta hanyar kulawa mai zurfi.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an sanar da wani rukuni na masu fama da cutar ta huhu da ba a san su ba, a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka, China ta sanar da cutar Novel Coronavirus, wanda yanzu ake kira da cutar ta Coronavirus ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an sanya ta sunan cutar Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Har zuwa yau, shaidar da aka samu ita ce, kashi 80% na mutanen da ke dauke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, wato, tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma mafi yawansu suna samun sauki.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari na shari'o'in, COVID-19 ya zama mafi munin cuta da ke buƙatar shiga asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin dari na shari'o'in ke da bayyanar cututtuka masu tsanani da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka kwantar da su asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin yaduwar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU / European Economic Area (EU / EEA) da kuma a cikin United Kingdom (UK) kuma mun kwatanta shi da lardin Hubei, China.
Muna kuma kwatanta adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu - 15 ga Maris, 2020 da na Italiya.
Kasashen EU/EEA da UK sun kamu da COVID-19
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da fadada a fannin duniya kuma a halin yanzu, ayyukan COVID-19 a sauran ƙasashe na duniya sun wuce wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris na shekarar 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na EuroSurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. an ruwaito farkon lamuran COVID-19 da aka tabbatar a Turai bisa ga ma'anar yanayin WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ruwaito farkon shari'o'i uku da aka tabbatar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da kuma United Kingdom (UK), tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 da aka ruwaito daga Italiya kadai tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da kuma ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da mutuwar 1,727 da aka ruwaito.
Samun adadin adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da kuma samun yaduwar yaduwarsu
A Cibiyar Tarayyar Turai don Rigakafin Cututtuka da Kulawa (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin COVID-19 daga kowace ƙasa a kowace rana a karfe 8:00 na safe, kawai daga tushen hukuma kamar su Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta ƙasashe, Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa da Kasa da WHO.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta su da cutar da ke faruwa a Italiya.
A matsayinmu na wakilin yaduwar shari'o'in COVID-19 masu aiki, mun ƙididdige taƙaitaccen yaduwar kwanaki 14 na shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin kowane EU/EEA ƙasa da Burtaniya, yayin da ake la'akari da tsarin halitta na COVID-19 a cikin lokacin 1 ga Janairu - 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma nuna jimlar adadin wadanda aka samu a kowace kasa da misalin karfe 8:00 na safe na ranar 15 ga watan Janairu - 15 ga watan Maris 2020 a lokacin da aka samu a kowace kasa da aka samu a lokacin 31 ga watan Janairu - 15 ga watan Maris 2020 a Italiya.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK
Yanayin da aka samu na kwanaki 14 na yaduwar yawan adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin kasashen EU/EEA da UK ya biyo bayan lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da kuma a cikin Burtaniya gabaɗaya, jimlar COVID-19 ta fara karuwa a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu kuma ta karu da sauri a kusa da 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (supplementary material).
Wannan ya kasance ne saboda yawan adadin wadanda aka samu daga Italiya, amma a duk sauran kasashen EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya, an samu irin wannan karuwar COVID-19 a cikin tarin yaduwar (supplementary material).
Hoton 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020 idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya.
Wannan ya nuna cewa a ranar 15 ga watan Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, sauran kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin shari'o'i da suka yi kama da na Italiya a makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 suna karuwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da Birtaniya.
Hanyoyin da aka lura a cikin yaduwar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa cutar ta kasance tana ƙaruwa a cikin ƙasashe duka.
Wannan duk da cewa akwai bambance-bambance a cikin matakan daban-daban na ƙasashe, bambance-bambance a cikin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, da kuma bambance-bambance a cikin ƙayyadaddun ma'anar shari'a da kuma yarjejeniyoyi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya a cikin ƙasashe waɗanda dole ne a bincika su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da kamawa da bincika su.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun ba da rahoton cewa, kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin yada labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da wuraren kula da marasa lafiya a wadannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar iyawarsu.
Bayanai na asibiti da/ko shigar da marasa lafiya a cikin ICU na COVID-19 a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'in, bi da bi (ba a nuna lambobin ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara su ta hanyar tsari don cika bayanan kulawa na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da yawan mutuwar.
A cikin binciken 2010-11, an lura da bambanci mai girma tsakanin samun gadon kulawa mai zurfi da gadon kulawa na matsakaici a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a Portugal a kowace yawan mutane 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa kasashe na iya samun albarkatu fiye da Italiya (da 12.5 cikin tsauraran kula da gado na matsakaici da kuma kula da mutane 100,000 a shekara ta 2010-11).
Yaduwar asibiti na COVID-19 da ke da alaƙa da 90% na haɗarin haɗarin ƙarfin gadon kulawa mai tsanani tare da kimantawa ga kowace EU/EEA ƙasa da UK ana ba da kwatancen yanayin haɗarin haɗarin haɗari na ECDC akan COVID-19 a cikin sabuntawa ta shida.
Tun da har yanzu akwai mutane da yawa a cikin EU/EEA da wasu yankunan Birtaniya da asibitoci da kuma wuraren kula da marasa lafiya da ke kula da marasa lafiya da ke kula da marasa lafiya da ke kula da marasa lafiya a wasu yankuna na EU/EEA, kuma asibitoci da wuraren kula da marasa lafiya suna kula da marasa lafiya a wasu yankuna na Burtaniya, dole ne a samar da bayanai game da marasa lafiya da wuraren kula da marasa lafiya a matakin Nomenclature of Territorial Units for Statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar da aka samu daga Italiya da kuma halin da ake ciki a sauran ƙasashe ya nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Kasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa mai zurfi ya kamata su shirya kansu don karuwar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar ci gaba da watsawar al'umma na SARS-CoV-2 da kuma kula da lafiya, musamman a yankunan da ke fama da cutar kamar yadda ake yi a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin binciken ECDC na kwanan nan, tare da sauya yanayin da ke ragewa zuwa ragewa, ana buƙatar hanzari, da hanzari da kuma zurfin ra'ayi don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, saboda idan ba a aiwatar da shi a kan lokaci ba, ƙila ba za a ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, yarda da kuma daidaita amsar su ba.
Har ila yau, ƙididdigar haɗari mai tsanani ta lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don kawar da tasirin cutar.
Kasashe suna da ƙananan dama don ƙara haɓaka ƙoƙarin sarrafa su da rage matsin lamba akan kiwon lafiya don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2.
Idan hakan bai yi nasara ba, zai yi kyau a ga tsarin kula da lafiya na sauran kasashen EU/EEA su fuskanci karuwar marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
A halin yanzu, cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ta haifar da cutar ta SARS (SARS) ta haifar da mutuwar mutane sama da 3,000 da kamuwa da cutar ta SARS (SARS) a kasar Sin da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da cutar ta SARS a dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya kamuwa da cutar ta bats kuma yana haifar da irin wannan alamun ta hanyar aiki.
