Halitta ta asali na kwayar cutar korona
Ta hanyar canji da kuma daidaitawa, an samo asali a cikin dubban shekaru na coronavirus (CoVs) da kuma abubuwan da ke gina jiki (ciki har da mutane).
Kafin 2003, an san akwai mutum biyu masu cutar sankara (HCoVs) wadanda ke haifar da cutar sanyi.
Fashewar cutar SARS da MERS sun nuna mummunan hali da cutar HCoV ta haifar da mummunan yanayi.
Yunƙurin SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ya sake kawo CoVs a fili kuma ya ba mu mamaki da ƙarancin kamuwa da cutar fiye da SARS-CoV 'yar'uwarta.
Cutar HCoV cuta ce ta dabbobi kuma fahimtar asalin dabbobi na HCoVs zai taimaka mana.
Yawancin HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga bats, wanda ba su da cutar.
Akwai kuma wasu bayanai game da abubuwan da ke cikin HCoVs.
Gano dabba yana da tasiri kai tsaye a cikin rigakafin cututtukan mutum.
Binciken hulɗar CoV-nutrient a cikin dabbobi na iya ba da mahimman bayanai game da kamuwa da cutar CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, muna gabatar da wani bayyani na bayanan yanzu game da HCoVs bakwai, tare da mayar da hankali kan tarihin binciken da aka samo asali da kuma watsawa ta hanyar dabbobi.
Abu mai mahimmanci, muna kwatanta HCoVs daban -daban kuma muna ganin bambance -bambance daga yanayin ci gaban kwayoyin halitta da kuma sake tsara kwayoyin halitta.
Ana tattauna cutar COVID-19 a cikin wannan hangen nesa na cutar ta yanzu.
Bugu da kari, an kuma nuna bukatar sauya abinci mai gina jiki da kuma tasirin ci gaban cutar a kan yadda cutar take da tsanani.
Kwayoyin cutar Corona (CoVs) na cikin iyalin Coronaviridae wanda ya hada da kungiyoyin kwayar RNA masu dauke da inganci, masu dauke da cutar, wadanda ke da nau'i daya.
Ana kiran wadannan kwayoyin da suka ba da mafaka ga mafi girma a cikin kwayoyin RNA, masu nauyin 26 zuwa 32 kilobes, CoVs saboda yanayin da ke ƙarƙashin lantarki.
A tsarin tsarin, CoVs suna da nau'in kwayoyin halitta marasa sashi waɗanda suke da tsari iri ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na genomes suna da manyan manyan manyan tsarin karantawa (ORF1a da ORF1b) waɗanda ke canzawa zuwa pp1a da pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Ana ci gaba da sarrafa polyprotein don samar da furotin 16 da ba na tsari ba, wanda ake kira nsp1~16.
Sauran kwayoyin halitta suna da ORFs don furotin na tsarin, ciki har da spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoproteins (N).
Hakanan ana sanya wasu furotin masu taimakawa na musamman ta hanyar tsarin zuriya daban -daban na CoVs.
Dangane da bambancin a cikin jerin sunadarai, CoV an rarraba shi zuwa ƙarni huɗu (Alpha-CoV, Beta-CoV, Gamma-CoV da Delta-CoV), daga cikinsu beta-CoVs ne mafi yawa a cikin ƙarni na HCoVs kuma an rarraba shi zuwa zuriya huɗu (A, B, C da D).
Shaidar ta nuna cewa bats da amphibians sune tushen asalin asalin alfanun alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye sune manyan kwayoyin gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoVs sun ci gaba da shawo kan matsalolin jinsin kuma sun fito a matsayin wasu muhimman cututtukan mutum.
Har zuwa yau, an san mutum bakwai na CoVs (HCoVs).
Daga cikinsu akwai HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 alpha-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoVs guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, mawuyacin cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), Coronavirus na numfashi mai tsanani na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 suna haifar da saukin bayyanar cututtuka kamar sanyi da/ko asarar zuciya.
Akasin haka, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da sabon gano SARS-CoV-2, suna da matukar cutarwa, suna haifar da kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar hanyar numfashi mai tsanani a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa tare da haɗarin haɗari mai tsanani na numfashi (ARDS) da bayyanar hyperpneumatic.
