Dole ne a sabunta ka'idodin asibiti na "masu zargin" da "masu tabbatar da" COVID-19
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagororin saurin tuntuɓar don ganewa da kuma magance kamuwa da cutar Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) ta 2019 kuma wannan jagorar ta samar da ƙwarewarmu da kuma daidaitaccen mahallin don magance cutar a duniya.
Koyaya, cutar Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, basirarmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali dangane da binciken bincike na yanzu da kuma kwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, ana sabunta dabarun bincike da magani akai-akai.
A cikin wannan wasiƙar, mun amsa wata tsokaci kan jagororinmu kuma mun samar da sabbin ka'idodin asibiti na "masu sharhi" da "masu tabbatarwa" daidai da sabon jagororin bincike da magani na COVID-19 (haɓaka ta bakwai) da Kwamitin Lafiya na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ya fitar.
A watan Disamba na 2019, an samu barkewar cutar Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) ta 2019 wanda yanzu aka sanya wa sunan cutar Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sanya wa cutar sunan cutar ta Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, WHO ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Don yaki da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta haɓaka jagororin shawarwari masu sauri waɗanda aka buga akan layi a cikin Nazarin Likitanci na Soja a ranar 06 ga Fabrairu 2020.
Tun lokacin da aka buga shi, ya sami babban kulawa.
Duk da haka, lura cewa COVID-19 sabon cuta ne, basirarmu da iliminmu suna karuwa a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike na yanzu da kuma kwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, ana sabunta dabarun bincike da magani akai-akai.
Misali, a total, an fitar da juzu'i bakwai tare da wasu canje -canje na asali a cikin wasu mahallin a cikin jagororin da Kwamitin Lafiya na Kasa na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ya fitar don ganewa da magance COVID-19 (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) tsakanin 16 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020.
