Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annobar duniya
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana barkewar cutar COVID-19 a matsayin annobar duniya.
Ko da yake kalmar "matsananci" tana nufin kawai yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda hatsarin da take fuskanta ba, WHO ta tattauna bukatar ta motsa gwamnatoci su dauki mataki.
Dukkanin kasashe na iya canza hanyar wannan annobar ta duniya.
Idan kasar ta amsa, za ta gano cutar, ta bi da marasa lafiya, ta ware su, ta gano su, ta haɗa su, in ji Tedros Adnanom Gebrazis, Darakta Janar na WHO.
