Hukumar kula da lafiyar al'umma ta lura da karuwar adadin wadanda aka tabbatar da su a ranar 20 ga Fabrairu, wanda ya danganta da taron jama'a a cikin Digo, wani sabon motsi na addini wanda aka sani da Babban cocin Yesu Shinchiji.
Shinchijiji masu zuwa daga Wuhan zuwa Daegu sun yi shakkar asalin cutar.
