Iran ta ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Kom a ranar 19 ga Fabrairu, inda mutane biyu suka mutu a ranar, a cewar Ma'aikatar Lafiya da Ilimin Likita.
Sauran matakan da gwamnati ta sanar sun hada da bukukuwa da sauran al'adu, wasanni da sallah na Juma'a, da rufe jami'o'i, cibiyoyin ilimi da makarantu.
Iran ta ba da tiriliyan biyar na riyal don magance cutar.
Shugaban kasa Hassan Rouhani ya ce a ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020, babu wani shiri na killace yankunan da cutar ta shafa kuma za a killace mutane ne kawai.
An sanar da shirin iyakance zirga -zirga tsakanin birane a watan Maris, duk da haka, har zuwa Nuwaros na Farisa, zirga -zirga mai yawa tsakanin birane ya ci gaba.
Har zuwa 16 ga Maris, 2020, wuraren haikalin Shia a Kom sun kasance a buɗe ga mahajjata. A lokacin Fabrairu, Iran ta zama cibiyar watsa kwayar bayan China.
A tsakanin da'awar ɓoye adadin barkewar cutar a Iran, fiye da kasashe goma sun gano cewa sun yi alaƙa da Iran a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, wanda ke nuna cewa adadin barkewar cutar na iya zama mafi tsanani fiye da 388 da gwamnatin Iran ta yi rikodin zuwa wannan ranar.
An rufe majalisar dokokin Iran a ranar 3 ga watan Maris, lokacin da aka tabbatar da cewa an samu kamuwa da cutar a 23 daga cikin mambobi 290 na majalisar.
A ranar 12 ga watan Maris, Human Rights Watch ta kuma bukaci hukumomin gidan yari na Iran da su saki 'yan kare hakkin bil adama da aka tsare a zaman lafiya don zanga-zangarsu ba tare da wani sharadi ba kuma su saki duk fursunonin da suka cancanci.
Ya ce, cibiyoyin da aka rufe kamar cibiyoyin hanawa suna da mafi girman haɗarin yaduwar cutar, wanda kuma ba shi da isasshen kulawar likita.
