Darakta Janar na WHO, Tedros Adnanom, ya ce, PHEIC na haifar da "hadarin yaduwar duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu karamin da matsakaitan kudade ba tare da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya ba.
